    ('Medu Vada', 'Mix the urad dal with 1 finely chopped onion, 1 green chilli, 1/2 tsp turmeric, 1/2 tsp chilli powder and salt; bind well; Shape into even portions, or dip in a thick gram-flour batter; Heat oil to 170-180C and fry in small batches 3-4 minutes until golden and crisp; Drain on paper towels; serve hot with green chutney', 'urad dal, gram flour, rice flour, green chilli, ginger, turmeric, salt, oil, coriander leaves'),
